# Local, per-developer agent working log — seeded from .ai/memory.example.md by `cargo xtask sync-ai`.
# Durable decisions go in commits / docs/adr, never here. See .ai/context.md "Memory protocol".
.ai/memory.md

# Secrets — never commit these.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Rust build artifacts.
/target/
**/target/
Cargo.lock.orig

# Generated example venues are reproducible from templates; the snapshot under
# crates/mf-codegen/tests/ is committed, ad-hoc generations are not.
/tmp-venue/
/my-clob/
/my-venue/

# Claude Code per-developer local settings (not shared).
.claude/settings.local.json

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store

# Demo recording tooling — kept local, not shipped. The rendered docs/imgs/demo.gif that the
# README embeds IS committed; the script and the intermediate asciinema cast are not.
scripts/record-demo.sh
docs/imgs/demo.cast
